nodes.text: Chiraneau was a human male who served as a Rear Admiral in the Imperial Navy of the Galactic Empire. At one point during the Imperial Era, Rear Admiral Chiraneau piloted a VT-49 Decimator, and also was stationed aboard the DS-2 Death Star II Mobile Battle Station shortly prior to the Battle of Endor. When Darth Vader arrived on the space station to check on the progress of construction, Chiraneau was one of many Imperial officers who stood at attention in a hangar as Vader disembarked and spoke with Moff Tiaan Jerjerrod.
